<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sv">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Admin — Referral-credits</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
  <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>🎁</text></svg>" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/gamification.css" />
  <style>
    .rc-wrap { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.25rem; }
    .rc-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .rc-header h1 { color: #f1f5f9; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
    .rc-header p { color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

    .rc-nav {
      display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .rc-nav a {
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: #cbd5e1; text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .rc-nav a:hover { border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.4); color: #f1f5f9; }

    .rc-saved {
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem; background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.25); border-radius: 10px;
      color: #34d399; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600;
    }

    .rc-card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e293b, #0f172a);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .rc-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .rc-table th, .rc-table td {
      padding: 0.75rem 0.5rem; text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .rc-table th {
      color: #a5b4fc; font-size: 0.72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; font-weight: 700;
    }
    .rc-table td { color: #cbd5e1; }
    .rc-table td.num {
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; text-align: right;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .rc-table td.num.pending { color: #34d399; }
    .rc-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .rc-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }

    .rc-empty {
      text-align: center; padding: 3rem 1rem;
      color: #64748b; font-style: italic;
    }

    .rc-inline {
      display: inline-flex; gap: 0.35rem; align-items: center;
    }
    .rc-inline input[type="number"] {
      width: 55px; padding: 0.35rem 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); color: #f1f5f9;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    .rc-btn {
      padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6);
      color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600;
    }
    .rc-btn:hover { filter: brightness(1.1); }

    .role-pill {
      display: inline-block; padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700;
    }
    .role-pill-free    { background: rgba(100,116,139,0.15); color: #94a3b8; }
    .role-pill-premium { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.15);   color: #4ade80; }
    .role-pill-pro     { background: rgba(251,191,36,0.15);  color: #fbbf24; }
    .role-pill-admin   { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.15);   color: #f87171; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="block-page">

  <main class="rc-wrap">

    <div class="rc-nav">
      <a href="/admin">← Admin</a>
      <a href="/admin/analytics">📊 Analytics</a>
    </div>

    <div class="rc-header">
      <h1>🎁 Referral-credits</h1>
      <p>
        Användare som intjänat gratismånader genom att värva betalande kunder.
        När du har applicerat krediten i Stripe (manuellt via kundportalen eller
        som kupong på nästa faktura), klicka "Markera utbetald" så bokförs det här.
      </p>
    </div>

    <% if (saved) { %>
      <div class="rc-saved">✓ Credit markerad som utbetald</div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="rc-card">
      <% if (!pending.length) { %>
        <div class="rc-empty">Inga pending credits just nu. Kom tillbaka när nya referrals konverterat.</div>
      <% } else { %>
        <table class="rc-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Användare</th>
              <th>Roll</th>
              <th class="num">Intjänade</th>
              <th class="num">Utbetalda</th>
              <th class="num">Pending</th>
              <th>Åtgärd</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% pending.forEach(function(u) { %>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <a href="/admin/user/<%= u.id %>" style="color:#a5b4fc;text-decoration:none;">
                    <%= u.username %>
                  </a>
                  <% if (u.email) { %>
                    <div style="color:#64748b;font-size:0.78rem;"><%= u.email %></div>
                  <% } %>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <span class="role-pill role-pill-<%= u.role %>">
                    <%= u.role === 'pro' ? '⚡ Pro' : u.role === 'premium' ? '✓ Premium' : u.role === 'admin' ? 'Admin' : 'Gratis' %>
                  </span>
                </td>
                <td class="num"><%= u.referral_credits_earned %></td>
                <td class="num"><%= u.referral_credits_redeemed %></td>
                <td class="num pending"><%= u.pending %></td>
                <td>
                  <form method="POST" action="/admin/users/<%= u.id %>/redeem-credits" class="rc-inline">
                    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>" />
                    <input type="number" name="count" min="1" max="<%= u.pending %>" value="<%= u.pending %>" required aria-label="Antal att markera" />
                    <button type="submit" class="rc-btn"
                            onclick="return confirm('Markera <%= u.pending %> credit(s) som utbetalda för <%= u.username %>? Gör detta EFTER du applicerat dem i Stripe.')">
                      Markera utbetald
                    </button>
                  </form>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% }); %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:1.5rem;padding:1rem 1.25rem;background:rgba(251,191,36,0.06);border-left:3px solid #fbbf24;border-radius:6px;color:#fef3c7;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.55;">
      💡 <strong>Arbetsflöde:</strong> Öppna användarens Stripe-kundprofil,
      lägg till en kupong eller credit på nästa faktura (199 kr för Premium,
      599 kr för Pro), kom sedan hit och klicka "Markera utbetald".
    </div>

  </main>

  <script src="/heartbeat.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
